attributes.Long form description: The student first grabs the lever and shifts it to the neutral position. Then, the student grabs the arm and tries to slide its end onto the peg but fails. The student rotates the end of the arm on several ocassions and tries to slide onto the peg but fails. The student keeps struggling to slide the arm onto the peg. The student briefly inspects the lever and tries to slide the arm onto the peg and fails again. The instructor asks the student if he put the lever in the neutral position; the student checks and confirms the lever is in the neutral position. The student tries to slide the arm onto the peg but keeps struggling. The instructor asks the student to shift the lever to the reverse position and the student does it. Then, the student tries to slide the arm onto the peg but fails again. The instructor asks the student to shift the lever to the park position and to try again. The student shifts the lever to the park position and then assembles the arm onto the peg.  The student goes to the parts bin area, approaches the left shelf and the instructor asks him to go to the one on the right. The student approaches the parts bin, grabs a washer and then goes to the left shelf. Then, the student is about to grab a bolt but the instructor asks him to grab one from the top left parts bin. The student inserts the bolt into the washer, approaches the arm and inserts the bolt into the peg. The student screws the bolt by hand. Then, goes to the tool car, grabs a ratchet and uses it to tighten the bolt. The student grabs the lever and checks the arm by shifting through all the gears. The student shifts the lever to park position, loosens the bolt with the ratchet and removes the bolt from the peg. The student drops the washer and picks it up again. The student places the ratchet on the tool car and shifts the lever back to the neutral position. The student goes to the parts bin area, approaches the left shelf and places the bolt into a parts bin. Finally, the student goes to the right shelf and places the washer into a parts bin.
